track.name: Poinciana
comments: Play this for your guests, then tell them it's the new Paul McCartney tune that was just released.
could listen to this for hours.
Les deux versions sont fabuleuses ; guitare ou non. Jamal, j'en suis givré !

Un absolu chef-d'oeuvre ! Le rythme transfigure la mélodie...Ici il n'y a plus l'un ou l'autre, ni l'un et l'autre non plus. L'osmose est complète. Jamal est un génie. L'on a envie de danser follement et de pleurer tout à la fois. Jeunesse et nostalgie mêlées.
I never get tired of hearing Ahmad play this tune.
still sooo good. so powerful, and smooth though.
did see him back in May at the Opera House.........wonderful music and he is so dignified
The one st the Pershing 1958 is definitely the best one
so far ahead of it's time
